content.name: NoSuperHighway
content.description:
Replaces the really fun superhighway with a load of nothing.
This is a Steam Workshop upload of Nexus Mod user stupidprocess' NoSuperHighway mod: https://www.nexusmods.com/x4foundations/mods/80
The title of this mod is a misnomer. It should be NoHighways, but I left the original name for the sake of attributing credit where credit is due.
This mod has been uploaded to the Steam Workshop with the original Author's permission
content.author: EagleDelta
